description: Released in 1994 by Marvel Music, this comic is a collaborative effort by artist Kyle Baker, hip-hop legend KRS-One, and Marshall Chess that uses literature and music to break the chains of ignorance among urban youth.  This issue comes polybagged with an audio cassette tape featuring songs performed by KRS-One that can be listened to as the comic is read.
name: BREAK THE CHAIN!
Zio Paperone e il campione in affitto
Paperino e gli ameboidi dello spazio profondo
C'era una volta... in America: Topolino e la legge del Far West
Ecco a Voi Orestolo il Papero!
Dois É Bom, Três É Demais
Quem Te Viu Já Não TV
Já Ganhou! Já Ganhou! Já Ganhou!
